org.knime.core.data.filestore.internal

Class LoopStartReferenceWriteFileStoreHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.core.data.filestore.internal.LoopStartReferenceWriteFileStoreHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFileStoreHandler, ILoopStartWriteFileStoreHandler, IWriteFileStoreHandler

    public final class LoopStartReferenceWriteFileStoreHandler
extends Object
implements ILoopStartWriteFileStoreHandler
    File store handler that is associated with a loop start node that is part of a loop body (nested loops). They delegate to the outer loop start node but also keep a history of which file stores were created in their (inner) loop execution to allow for a cleanup after each iteration.
    Author:
    Bernd Wiswedel, KNIME.com, Zurich, Switzerland
